[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-2008","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-2008.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1576","title":"Adobe Acrobat ActiveX控件 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Adobe Acrobat 4.0 阅读器所捆绑的 Adobe Acrobat ActiveX 控件（pdf.ocx，ProgID 为 PDF.PdfCtrl.1，版本 1.3.188）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该控件在处理 pdf.setview 方法传入的参数时未进行充分的长度校验，导致超长输入可覆盖内存缓冲区。远程攻击者只需构造一个恶意网页或 HTML 文档，诱导受害者使用 Internet Explorer 等支持 ActiveX 的浏览器打开，即可触发该漏洞并在目标用户权限下执行任意代码。受影响范围为安装 Acrobat Reader 4.0 且加载该 ActiveX 控件的 Windows 系统，攻击无需身份认证，利用门槛较低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1576"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:45.407","remediation":"立即卸载 Adobe Acrobat Reader 4.0，升级至 Adobe Acrobat Reader DC (2024.005.20320 或更高版本) 或 Foxit Reader 等现代 PDF 阅读器。若必须使用旧版本，请在 IE/Edge 中禁用 \"Adobe PDF Reader ActiveX 控件\" (pdf.ocx) 并禁用 PDF 文件在浏览器中打开，同时在防火墙层面拦截恶意 PDF 下载链接作为临时缓解。建议通过 Adobe 官网或官方更新通道获取最新版本。立即部署补丁并清理已受感染系统的恶意 PDF 文件。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/25919","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/28719","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/666","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3318","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19514","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2218edc43f34225d168835de417dff40749bef5/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1576.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1576","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1576.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1576.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6cpp-p296-85wp/GHSA-6cpp-p296-85wp.json","https://github.com/buffer/phoneyc/blob/d566bd12e70da0ccd952e69e2b02922c7ab61797/ActiveX/modules/PDFsetview","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1576.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_3.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-2008.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-2008.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-2008.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0737","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0737.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0940","title":"Mutt 邮件客户端 缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"mutt 邮件客户端在处理特制的 MIME 消息时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送包含恶意构造的 MIME 附件的电子邮件，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在受害者系统上执行任意代码。该漏洞影响多个版本的 mutt 邮件客户端，攻击者无需身份认证即可利用，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0940"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-27T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:22.293","remediation":"立即将 mutt 升级到 0.95.7 及以上修复版本（1999 年官方补丁修复了 MIME 解析中的缓冲区溢出）。若暂时无法升级，可在邮件客户端配置中禁用自动执行外部 MIME 处理器、关闭 HTML/附件自动渲染，并改用 less 等安全查看器预览邮件以缓解风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0940","https://github.com/trickest/cve/blob/638563f1ec085a412c2e42f3935801ae34f0dfd9/1999/CVE-1999-0940.md","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/aa3114da1227373bef7855dba21bcaa5f0e0ad76/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0940.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0940","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4d2ed764072119c12b6f84e6ee4e0df62586a8c4/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0940.json","https://github.com/mabitoski/cve_submodules/blob/44ad7e2705b3aef1b2ffaf64bd47596c10a6c2e4/1999/CVE-1999-0940.md","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/bf2339193e1c10dc2db330718adeb8cc8d88c4dd/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-pm3w-22f3-8w8x/GHSA-pm3w-22f3-8w8x.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0940.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0737.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0522","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0522.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0788","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9125,\"outputTokens\":29,\"totalTokens\":10818}}","description":"Knox Software Arkeia 备份软件的 nlserverd 服务（4.0 与 4.1 版本）存在拒绝服务漏洞。该服务在处理远程客户端请求时未能正确校验输入，导致攻击者可通过向目标主机上 nlserverd 监听的端口发送特制的数据包触发异常，使服务崩溃或停止响应。未经身份认证的远程攻击者可利用此漏洞对运行受影响版本的 Arkeia 服务器发起远程拒绝服务攻击，导致合法备份与管理操作中断，影响系统可用性。利用方式简单，无需认证且无需本地访问权限，仅需网络可达即可发送恶意请求。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0788"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-26T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.567","remediation":"建议升级 Knox Software Arkeia 至 4.2 及以上修复版本，或应用厂商针对 nlserverd 发布的安全补丁。如暂无法升级，可在防火墙或边界设备上过滤到达 5555 端口（nlserverd 服务端口）的非法/异常外部连接，仅允许受信任内部主机访问，以缓解远程拒绝服务风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93837184228248&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/662","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/19dfa989c2a07b8fd71870a139a7d171f621ff41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0788.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0788","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0788.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9ef5a1e2753195eb4be450895da310f7a8a6524e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0788.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-29xc-rhpj-gjp7/GHSA-29xc-rhpj-gjp7.json","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/sid-msg.map","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/jdkoftinoff/mb-linux-msli/blob/8adb103e34af9ff1d8d122e9ee2a1808836f0a14/uClinux-dist/user/snort/drop-rules/dos.rules","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0788.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.193"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0522.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1909","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1909.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1484","title":"Microsoft MSN Messenger Service Setup BBS ActiveX 控件缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Microsoft MSN Messenger Service 1.0 Setup BBS 组件中的 setupbbs.ocx ActiveX 控件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过诱使用户访问恶意网页或打开恶意文件，调用该控件的 vAddNewsServer 或 bIsNewsServerConfigured 方法并传入超长参数，触发缓冲区溢出，从而在目标系统上执行任意命令。该漏洞影响运行 MSN Messenger Service 1.0 Setup BBS 4.71.0.10 的 Windows 系统，攻击者无需身份验证即可远程利用，危害等级为高危（CVSS 7.5）。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1484"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:32.423","remediation":"立即卸载或禁用 MSN Messenger Service 1.0 自带的 Setup BBS ActiveX 控件（setupbbs.ocx，版本 4.71.0.10），在 Internet Explorer 中通过“管理加载项”将该控件设为禁用并不允许运行。升级到已修复此问题的 Microsoft MSN Messenger 后续版本（3.0 及以上），同时在企业网络中通过组策略限制 ActiveX 控件运行以降低远程代码执行风险。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/28719","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/668","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3310","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19516","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/73dad9db65989a09e468a4f3a98f0eea36f0346c/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1484.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1484","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1484.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/5297adfba5e91ee22e711c26c523b292d427c0d0/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1484.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-7697-hr74-2qhh/GHSA-7697-hr74-2qhh.json","https://github.com/xqcyberscore/nvt/blob/978f6a9acb495d7d669239530ffe6da5d631f4da/pre2008/winmessenger_installed.nasl","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1484.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_1.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000791.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1909.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1909.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1909.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1196","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1196.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1578","title":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.1/5 Registration Wizard ActiveX 控件缓冲区溢出代码执行漏洞","description":"Microsoft Internet Explorer 4.01 与 5.0 中内置的 Registration Wizard ActiveX 控件（regwizc.dll，版本 3.0.0.0，公开方法 InvokeRegWizard）存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该控件在处理远程传入的参数时未对输入长度进行边界校验，攻击者在网页或 HTML 邮件中构造恶意页面，诱导用户访问即可触发溢出，进而覆盖栈上返回地址并执行任意命令。影响范围涵盖 IE 4.01 及 5.0 浏览器用户，利用前提是被害者需使用 IE 并打开攻击者控制的页面，属于需要用户交互的远程代码执行漏洞。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1578"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:45.670","remediation":"升级 Internet Explorer 至 5.01 Service Pack 2 或更高版本（包含在 Windows 2000 SP2 及后续补丁中）。如无法立即升级，可在 Internet Explorer 的「工具→Internet 选项→安全」中将 Internet 区域的安全级别设为「高」，并禁用对 regwizc.dll（Registration Wizard ActiveX 控件）的 ActiveX 运行与脚本权限，或在组策略中限制该控件的实例化作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.kb.cert.org/vuls/id/37556","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/28719","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/671","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3311","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19528","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/e2218edc43f34225d168835de417dff40749bef5/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1578.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1578","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1578.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/2119b082f4927b0a9c902ed9fe95efb3b301cb81/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1578.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/d94ad47d0f2016e121b6d251f490e890714f8916/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8wmp-mpx8-hrwf/GHSA-8wmp-mpx8-hrwf.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1578.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000792.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--fd4caeb6-7cb4-4970-80aa-36baa776bee5.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-1196.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-1196.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1196.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1068","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1068.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1351","title":"KVIrc IRC客户端 目录遍历任意文件读取漏洞","description":"KVIrc IRC 客户端 0.9.0 版本在处理 DCC GET 请求时存在目录遍历漏洞。当用户启用了 \"Listen to !nick <soundname> requests\" 选项后，远程攻击者可通过向目标 IRC 客户端发送包含 `..`（点点）序列的特制 DCC GET 请求，突破文件路径限制，实现任意文件读取。攻击者无需身份认证即可利用此漏洞窃取目标系统上的敏感文件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1351"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-24T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:15.337","remediation":"升级 KVIrc 至 1.0.0 或更高版本，该漏洞已在后续版本中修复。如无法升级，请在「设置」→「选项」→「IRC」→「高级」中取消勾选「Listen to !nick &lt;soundname&gt; requests」选项以禁用该功能，并避免在不可信频道中接受 DCC 请求。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93845560631314&w=2","http://www.iss.net/security_center/static/7761.php","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/f4ffb7bcd93209aa53a757a7ebdf17fe2a18eb33/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1351.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1351","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-1351.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/bcb2bc8aed064ca80cf72b28e99ae813ae48a2c2/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1351.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/e434c1da6464de3012c6c1eff8c0e19ef9669023/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-8p4w-cwr7-jq9h/GHSA-8p4w-cwr7-jq9h.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1351.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000790.txt","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/Yuning-J/VulnerabilityClassifier/blob/c0f06c21b73c26b5ee2b75c21a498eb04eada4b5/threatPrediction/cveIDThreatType/cve_iddirtra"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1068.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1126","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1126.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1477","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9199,\"outputTokens\":42,\"totalTokens\":10905}}","description":"Mandriva Linux Mandrake 6.0 及 GNOME Libraries 1.0.8 中的 espeaker 程序存在本地缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者通过向 nethack 等程序传递超长的 --espeaker 参数，触发栈缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址实现任意代码执行，从而将本地用户权限提升至 root 权限。该漏洞影响 Mandrake 6.0 及使用 GNOME Libraries 1.0.8 的 Linux 发行版，攻击者需具备本地账户访问权限，通过构造超长参数字符串触发栈溢出并劫持控制流获取 root 权限。CVSS 评分 7.2，属高危本地提权漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1477"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:50:31.527","remediation":"建议立即升级 GNOME 库至 1.0.8 以上修补版本，或升级 Mandriva Linux Mandrake 至 6.1 及以上版本。若暂无法升级，可通过 `chmod u-s /usr/games/nethack` 移除 nethack 等易受攻击程序的 setuid 位，或限制本地用户执行权限作为临时缓解措施。建议访问 Mandriva 官方安全公告获取官方补丁包进行升级。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/28717","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/663","https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/3349","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19512","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/5b55afba6f3a87fe9319e1de76170e4c2760d614/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1477.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1477","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1477.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1477.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/90b464bbc2d1b64270a5771429f96b67fbe9e79b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-6fm6-5ph4-2rpq/GHSA-6fm6-5ph4-2rpq.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Exploit-List-Ja/blob/979579ffd61606c64cf772a1e865f5126788e4ec/1999.tsv","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_4.list.dict","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/134977c5f4ce4f427a914ca161b4f075e34b560b/nvdcve/CVE-1999-1477.json","https://github.com/hungryfoolou/Vulnerability_Mining/blob/3df1d8ed0489ae1228f975ae1f58a690aae53886/craw/cveid_craw/cveid_craw/data/cveid_by_kind/cveid_overflow.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1126.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0863","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0863.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1013","title":"{\"_meta\":{},\"stopReason\":\"end_turn\",\"usage\":{\"cachedReadTokens\":1664,\"inputTokens\":9135,\"outputTokens\":17,\"totalTokens\":10816}}","description":"AIX named-xfer 组件存在文件覆盖漏洞，系统组成员可通过 -f 参数指定恶意构造的区域文件，利用 named-xfer 处理区域传输时的权限缺陷覆盖任意系统文件，进而实现本地提权至 root。该漏洞影响 AIX 4.1.5 和 4.2.1 版本，攻击者需具备系统组权限并能访问 named-xfer 程序，通过精心设计的畸形区域文件触发漏洞，CVSS 评分 7.2，属于高危本地提权漏洞。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1013"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:31.357","remediation":"建议升级 AIX 至 IBM 官方修复版本（4.3.2 或更高），或安装 IBM 针对 named-xfer 发布的 APAR 补丁（IX72659）。若无法立即升级，可移除 named-xfer 的 setuid/setgid 权限（chmod u-s,g-s /usr/sbin/named-xfer），并限制 system 组成员，禁止普通用户通过 -f 参数指定任意区域文件路径。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93837026726954&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/673","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/0e46881568ba1d1c2011ec61282a082880cda856/cves/1999/1xxx/CVE-1999-1013.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-1013","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-1013.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/57cb981038a97031bd95a35a9b10bbed18ca4725/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-1013.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-958c-wvqf-f46f/GHSA-958c-wvqf-f46f.json","https://github.com/SpeeDr00t/speedr00t.github.com/blob/0380f0c2190556fabe90257cb6c0034a42f68951/securityfocus/0x1000/673/info.html","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-1013.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/dong-xs/Vul-PAG/blob/7eb3b32094a5270cfd8495366e0e4a7df5a874ce/aspect_prediction/org_pred_diff.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/fd4916152066cf69446b0fbd8f7bb3a97a137e13/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0863.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0708","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0708.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0777","title":"Microsoft IIS FTP 安全绕过漏洞","description":"IIS（Internet Information Server）及 Commercial Internet System 的 FTP 服务存在权限校验绕过漏洞。由于 FTP 服务器对用户访问权限的处理逻辑存在缺陷，远程攻击者即使被设置为\"无访问权限（No Access）\"，仍可通过构造恶意 FTP 请求绕过权限限制，非法读取或删除服务器上的文件。该漏洞影响运行上述 FTP 服务的 Windows 系统，攻击者可利用匿名或低权限 FTP 连接即可远程发起攻击，无需身份认证，危害较大。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0777"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-23T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:02.220","remediation":"建议升级至 IIS 6.0 或更高版本并安装微软安全补丁 MS99-025；在 IIS 管理器中为 FTP 站点移除匿名用户的\"No Access\"权限，改为显式拒绝访问；若暂无法升级，请在防火墙层面限制 FTP 端口(21/TCP)仅允许受信 IP 访问，并禁用匿名 FTP 登录作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ241407","http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ242559","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/658","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-039","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/8981d7e7baa3f6c5d7a90cd823433b0422b8fcd2/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0777.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0777","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0777.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/94e644a0057439310dc2677c2e4ebd7766be1682/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0777.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/958f1672375e115879b3a6bd13e3638812260c7d/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-qjvq-8mcw-xc4h/GHSA-qjvq-8mcw-xc4h.json","https://github.com/marcellodesales/aibbp-reverse-engineer/blob/960f610d597aae9fec1cc5f03c68679be00c222d/reverse_engineer/acunetix/vulnerabilities/vdb/1999/0xxx/cve-1999-0777.yaml","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0777.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0708.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0708.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1167","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1167.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-1534","title":"Knox Software Arkeia 备份套件 nlservd 和 rnavc 本地缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Knox Software Arkeia 备份产品中的 nlservd 和 rnavc 组件存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。攻击者可通过设置超长 HOME 环境变量触发缓冲区溢出，成功利用可获取 root 权限。该漏洞影响 SuSE Linux 6.2 等多个操作系统平台。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-1534"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-23","updated":"2024-11-20","remediation":"升级到 Knox Software 官方修复版本，或移除 nlservd 和 rnavc 的 SUID 权限位以防止本地提权。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T16:53:33.188326258+00:00","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93837184228248&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/661"],"poc_urls":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93837184228248&w=2"],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1167.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0710","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0710.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0908","title":"Sun Solaris TCP Stream Driver 递归 mutex_enter 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Sun Solaris 2.5.1/2.6/7.0 的 TCP 流驱动中存在拒绝服务漏洞，远程攻击者可通过 nmap OS 指纹识别选项（-O）向开放端口发送恶意连接，当目标服务进程被终止后，TCP 流驱动中的 mutex_enter 函数发生递归调用，导致系统内核崩溃重启。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0908"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-09-23","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级 Solaris 系统至不受影响的版本，或安装 Sun 官方发布的安全补丁，限制对 TCP 端口的未授权访问，使用防火墙过滤恶意连接以防止利用 nmap OS 指纹识别触发递归 mutex_enter 调用导致系统崩溃","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/655","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19507"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0710.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0705","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0705.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0906","title":"S.u.S.E. Linux 6.2 sccw HOME环境变量缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"S.u.S.E. Linux 6.2 中的 sccw 程序存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。该程序在处理 HOME 环境变量时未对长度进行正确检查，本地攻击者可通过设置过长的 HOME 环境变量触发栈缓冲区溢出，覆盖返回地址，从而获取 root 权限。攻击需要本地用户身份，无需特殊权限。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0906"],"sources":["cve","exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-23","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"升级到 S.u.S.E. Linux 6.2 的官方补丁版本，或限制本地用户对 sccw 程序的执行权限。由于该产品已停止支持，建议迁移到受支持的 Linux 发行版。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-19T00:00:00Z","references":["https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0906","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19508","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/656"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19508"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19508"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0705.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0519","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0519.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0786","title":"Sun Solaris 动态链接器 LD_PROFILE 符号链接攻击漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.6 动态链接器存在文件创建漏洞，本地攻击者可通过设置 LD_PROFILE 环境变量并结合符号链接攻击，利用动态链接器的权限创建任意文件。该漏洞允许低权限用户以提升的权限在系统任意位置写入文件，可能导致权限提升或系统破坏。攻击需要本地用户身份且对系统有基本访问权限，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0786"],"sources":["exploitdb"],"published":"1999-09-22T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.317","remediation":"在 /etc/ld.so.conf 中注释掉 LD_PROFILE 设置，修改 /etc/profile 文件限制 LD_DEBUG 使用，并设置安全环境变量 LD_DEBUG=0 用于限制动态链接器功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/659","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19509","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/abfccbe3a11aa2b9dde2cfba5a12ba6256820a51/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0786.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0786","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/e046e4965f64348bd29a0c62edd023b3c580939e/content/CVE-1999-0786.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/ed6bb242e8dd7e27b54cbf189349b0ad2ae7c304/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0786.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/780ea229276a503f17a45c7ccc9fc5e26e6b2447/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-2whr-5263-qqgc/GHSA-2whr-5263-qqgc.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153600_153700.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0786.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_2.list.dict","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0519.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0712","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0712.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0912","title":"FreeBSD vfs_cache 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"FreeBSD 操作系统的 VFS 文件系统缓存（vfs_cache）机制存在资源耗尽缺陷。具有本地账户权限的攻击者可以通过在系统中打开大量文件描述符来消耗内核文件缓存资源和文件表项，导致系统缓存溢出或文件表耗尽，从而使合法用户无法正常创建或访问文件，造成服务拒绝。该漏洞影响 FreeBSD 2.x 及 3.x 早期版本，攻击条件为攻击者已拥有本地 shell 访问权限且系统未施加文件描述符数量限制。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0912"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-09-22","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:18.920","remediation":"将受影响的 FreeBSD 系统升级到 3.3-RELEASE 或更高版本，该版本已修复 vfs_cache 文件描述符资源耗尽缺陷。如暂无法升级，可通过 login.conf 中配置 openfiles 参数限制普通用户可同时打开的文件描述符数量，并收紧本地账户权限，减少非授权用户获取 shell 的机会，以此作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-17T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1079","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/653","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0912"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0712.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0712.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0712.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0521","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0521.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0787","title":"SSH Communications Security SSH 1.2.27 认证代理符号链接漏洞","description":"SSH Communications Security 公司出品的 SSH 1.2.27 版本中，ssh-agent 认证代理在创建用于身份认证的 UNIX 域套接字文件时，未对路径进行符号链接检查。本地攻击者可在 agent 预期创建 socket 的目录下预先放置一个指向任意目标文件（如 ~/.rhosts 或系统关键配置文件）的符号链接。当 agent 启动并跟随该符号链接创建套接字文件时，会以当前用户权限在符号链接指向的位置创建或覆盖文件，从而篡改受保护文件内容，可能造成权限提升或账户被非法信任。该漏洞为本地利用型，攻击条件要求攻击者在目标主机上拥有普通用户账户并能控制文件系统布局，影响范围仅限于 SSH 1.2.27 版本，CVSS 基础评分为 2.1，危害程度较低。","severity":"LOW","score":2.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0787"],"sources":["epss"],"published":"1999-09-17T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:03.440","remediation":"建议立即升级 SSH Communications Security SSH 至 1.2.28 或更高版本（该版本已修复认证代理跟随符号链接的问题）。如暂无法升级，可手动设置 SSH_AUTH_SOCK 指向仅当前用户可写的专用目录（如 ~/.ssh-agent），并以 chmod 700 限制该目录权限，禁止其他用户创建符号链接；同时避免在共享或不可信目录中运行 ssh-agent 以作临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-18T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93760201002154&w=2","http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93832856804415&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/660","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19510","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/19dfa989c2a07b8fd71870a139a7d171f621ff41/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0787.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0787","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/5cf8ba64f356efe9269b21eca2f657231acd746c/content/CVE-1999-0787.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/9ef5a1e2753195eb4be450895da310f7a8a6524e/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0787.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/f61040ac78eb76aff0a3a68a8a8a4562940d3711/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-93v8-gx5g-v586/GHSA-93v8-gx5g-v586.json","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0787.json","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--76e0f930-9120-4d0c-b52e-6cf26ac3a600.json","https://github.com/security-commits/security-patches-dataset/blob/e93fcdcc8c9b91785f962a06d66b7ee623780245/data/cve-details/year/1999.csv","https://github.com/nomi-sec/CVE-Easy-List/blob/95667eace3f4d053cefbe6b54fe10b3647ab0f79/1999.tsv"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/pocs/1999/POC-AVE-1999-0521.toml"],"repo_exp_urls":["https://raw.githubusercontent.com/adysec/AVE/main/exploits/1999/EXP-AVE-1999-0521.toml"],"has_poc":true,"has_exp":true,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0521.toml"}]